review_blob: mandarin hops, pale lager, tasted at Vessel 11 (v11) Rotterdam during the introduction. Pours a tad bit cloudy but has a extremely refreshing taste to it. Der Kaiser got it richtig with this one.
Amazingly smooth. Bit hazy but boy what a well balanced criso IPA. Poured from draft. Boy Im lucky to be so close to a bar that has this stuff on tap.
Really clear. Full body, poors almost like chocolate milk. I love this one.
